---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy — calóh"
  description="Privacy policy for calóh studio."
>
  <main>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="prose-page">
        <h1 class="page-heading">Privacy</h1>
        <p class="page-date">Last updated: March 2026</p>

        <h2>Data we collect</h2>
        <p>
          We do not collect names, emails, or form submissions on this site.
        </p>

        <h2>Analytics</h2>
        <p>
          We use <strong>PostHog</strong> for anonymous traffic analytics. PostHog is
          configured without personal data collection (<code>person_profiles: 'never'</code>),
          uses in-memory persistence only, and respects Do Not Track preferences.
          No cross-site tracking occurs.
        </p>

        <h2>Cookies</h2>
        <p>
          We do not set advertising or tracking cookies. A single entry in
          <code>localStorage</code> may be written to remember your theme preference
          (light or dark). This value is local to your browser and is never transmitted
          to any server.
        </p>

        <h2>Data sharing</h2>
        <p>
          We do not sell or share personal data with any third party.
        </p>

        <h2>Data retention</h2>
        <p>
          Anonymous analytics aggregates are retained to understand general usage patterns.
          Email correspondence sent to us is kept only as long as necessary to respond.
        </p>

        <h2>Your rights (EU/EEA)</h2>
        <p>
          If you are located in the EU or EEA, you have the right to access, correct,
          or request deletion of any personal data we hold. Contact us and we will
          respond within 30 days.
        </p>

        <h2>Changes</h2>
        <p>
          This policy may be updated. The latest version is always available at{' '}
          <a href="/privacy/">/privacy/</a>.
        </p>

        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>
          <a href="mailto:calohstudio@pm.me">calohstudio@pm.me</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
